# Prebuilt viewer artifact — committed so `/plugin install` (a git clone) needs
# no `bun run build` step (plan 016). Re-included despite the generic `dist/`
# rule above. Rebuilt by CI + scripts/release.sh; grammar chunks are
# content-hashed and stable, so a UI-source change only rewrites the small core
# chunk, not the ~300 syntax grammars. Treated as generated in .gitattributes.
!src/ui/dist/
!src/ui/dist/**
